        <h4><a class="taggedlink linklink" href="http://news.yahoo.com/s/ap/20070220/ap_on_go_ot/terror_prosecutions">Audit: Anti-terror case data flawed - Yahoo! News</a></h4>

        
            
        

        <p>&#8220;Federal prosecutors counted immigration violations, marriage fraud and drug trafficking among anti-terror cases in the four years after 9/11 even though no evidence linked them to terror activity, a Justice Department audit said Tuesday.&#8221;</p>

