<h3 class="date"><a href="/2006/jul/08/">&#x27a0;</a> July 8, 2006</h3>


<div class="row">
    <div class="span12">


    
    <div class="well" id="get_your_priori" >

        
        <a name="002671"></a>
        

        <h4><a class="taggedlink linklink" href="http://www.opinionjournal.com/editorial/feature.html?id=110008626">Get Your Priorities Right: A rationalist crusader does the math on global warming.</a></h4>

        

        <p>I&#8217;ve been impressed with Bjorn Lomborg since reading an article he wrote in The Economist on the Kyoto agreement five years ago.  Here, he argues that, while global warming is a problem, it should be a fantastically low priority for funding compared to AIDS or Malaria.</p>

